'''Emergency Strategic Option Six''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] computer-derived logic response to a combat situation involving excessively uneven odds. The option called for the immediate surrender of affected forces to opposing adversaries.

The ranking officer in charge of the Imperial outpost at [[Spindrift]] enacted Emergency Strategic Option Six when he found himself outmaneuvered by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] forces in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]].

